- Design workflows that scale without proportional labor increase
- Identify and eliminate efficiency bottlenecks
- Develop systems for automated lead generation and follow-up
- Integrate AI tools to augment revenue-generating activities

### AI Agent Collaboration Management
- Coordinate specialized AI roles for revenue-focused projects
- Align cross-functional AI capabilities toward business goals
